        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7787_p4">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>
          <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName>,</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7787_p5">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>Sir,</p>
      </div>
    </front>
    <body>
            <div>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7787_p6">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>May I beg of you to write me a reply to my
       <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>letter of the <date when="1872-07-08">8<hi rend="sup">th</hi> July</date>, asking for certain information
       <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>necessary to submit my offer for the <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Saint Gothard</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>contract in the form you wish. –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7787_p7">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>I am somewhat at a loss to understand
       <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>this delay as you have so often impressed me
       <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>with the necessity that existed for losing no 
       <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>time: – I beg to point out to you the absolute
       <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>necessity there is to get the question of the Contract
       <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>decided at once, or it will be too late to do any<lb break="no" xml:id="p1-l19"/>thing on the mountain this season and
       <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>another year will be lost.</p>
    </div>
        </body>
    <back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7787_p8">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>I have the honor to be
        <lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>Sir
        <lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>Your obedient <choice>
                        <abbr>Serv<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Servant (Diener)</expan>
                    </choice>
                </p>
      </div>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7787_p9">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>Fred Beaumont.
        <lb xml:id="p1-l25"/>Chairman of <choice>
                        <abbr>M. T. Co<hi rend="sup">y</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Mountain Tunnel Company</expan>
                    </choice>
                </p> </div>
